WEBVTT

00:00:07.628 --> 00:00:11.090
Vaš plan da spojite 
prijateljicu Carey i poznanika Emersona

00:00:11.090 --> 00:00:13.259
napokon uspijeva.

00:00:13.259 --> 00:00:15.887
Oboje su čuli puno
jedno o drugome

00:00:15.887 --> 00:00:17.680
i žele se naći na večeri.

00:00:17.680 --> 00:00:20.183
Baš ste im rezervirali stol 
za petak navečer,

00:00:20.183 --> 00:00:22.310
i samo što niste Carey
poslali detalje,

00:00:22.310 --> 00:00:25.063
kada se sjetite nečega uznemirujućeg:

00:00:25.063 --> 00:00:27.106
Carey uvijek kasni.

00:00:27.106 --> 00:00:29.108
I to ne samo 5 minuta;

00:00:29.108 --> 00:00:31.652
ponekad 20 ili čak 30 minuta.